00:21:53.130 --> 00:21:55.130
I wanted to get to know you better

00:21:55.130 --> 00:21:55.960
Hey hey

00:21:55.960 --> 00:21:57.500
The early bird catches you know what

00:21:57.500 --> 00:22:00.460
I wanna see deeper, deeper, deeper

